# ⭐ 这篇里的高级表达（直接背）

## 描述“占比最高”

> making it the most common destination

> recorded the highest proportion of employees

---

## 描述“集中于某区间”

> were more concentrated in the middle-income range

这个特别高级。

以后：

* age groups
* salary ranges
* spending categories

都能用。

